description:
The RabbitMQ .NET client is the official client library for C# (and, implicitly, other .NET languages), compatible with RabbitMQ 2.0 or later versions (some features may only be available in 3.x)
      This version of the RabbitMQ.Client assembly can be loaded as an assembly into the SQL Server CLR.   Notably, the WinRT components have been removed.   You should only use this package if you need
      to author a SQL Server CLR routein that needs access to RabbitMQ.
summary: RabbitMQ.Client library that can run in the Sql Server CLR
title: RabbitMQ.SqlServerClr.Client
